data.title: Find your Supervisor of Elections by list
data.text:
Find your County

You can find your county by selecting your city in the box (lower left), immediately after selecting your city your county will display on the lower right.

HINT: For a faster selection of your city click the down arrow on the city box then type the first letter of your city you will then be taken to the first city that starts with the letter you typed in. Preferred browser for viewing is Chrome.
